Known problems:

1.

When compiled with gcc 4.6 from ports, static boost libraries compiled
with apple gcc causes errors:

sup(38484) malloc: *** error for object 0x7fff7f191860: pointer being freed was not allocated
*** set a breakpoint in malloc_error_break to debug
Abort trap: 6


See:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4697859/mac-os-x-and-static-boost-libs-stdstring-fail

